Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們置身於日本第一峰 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要攀登山頂 觀看日出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在向正八合目的登山小屋出發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.33,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士山才沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切身感到身在山中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 好像不是現實 像是在夢裡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山頂看日出的時候 更像在夢境呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 要爬這麼陡峭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪算路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖鍊只是指示方向用的 不能抓喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為空氣稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐著不動也喘不過氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八合目 剛剛就近在眼前了 但怎麼爬 都爬不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按自己的節奏爬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的 慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 大家也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小葵 沒事吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到 大家的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真夠累的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這麼累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好陡峭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到八合目了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把勁 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九合目下面還有正八合目和八合目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 要不要吃點花林糖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有黑糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實還有羊羹和綠茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟老爺爺一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去烙印回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小葵學姐的一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說當年聖德太子就住這間小屋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史真悠久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相傳聖德太子當年是騎飛馬來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是太子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 小葵 說是騎馬飛上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說裡面的燒水壺是200年前的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,200年前是江戶時代！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向 可可娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個先去預定好的正八合目的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是高山症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先在這看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的話就繼續往上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵學姐 我們先往上爬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息一下再來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很好吃的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐 我們先上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下我們兩個人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 一開始還那麼有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想了 現在只管往上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡思亂想解決不了問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先盡全力做好眼前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在正八合目等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向和可可娜醬先出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟這間小屋說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進去躺下好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向她們先走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 頭痛完全沒有好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好陡峭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是在走 但喘得像百米衝刺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是空氣稀薄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐說過 做深呼吸比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說吹口哨也比較有效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安到了啊 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃過飯早點休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡沒事的話 就夜裡出發攻頂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵學姐怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐說不用擔心 好轉之後夜裡出發攻頂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓癟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mike. Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey come on! And remenber?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when that guy asked you to do that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I say no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you gotta do it, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, I can't do that thing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When someone ask you to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got in so much trouble after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出發勉強能趕上日出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是誰害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼叫都叫不醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快兩點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點就趕不上到山頂看日出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 先冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都努力爬到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞強往上爬 萬一回不去了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山又不會跑掉 想挑戰多少次都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再穿一件比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜醬 你這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓絨衣 很暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都穿得好臃腫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各種職業的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有外國人的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都爬到這裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐傳訊來 說要我們連小葵的份一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小葵那份一起爬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡黑夜跟城裡完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是自然裡的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是太慢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢點也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願小葵學姐也在看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想親眼一見 但實際和想像中的不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像色斑一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘不過氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心情激動 連疲勞都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空已經發白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 心情激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要睡袋 好想在床上睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}待續
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:04.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 不思議と どうしてかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:12.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミが笑うと 心の奥いつもキラリまたたく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's little step! 一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's feel skip! 一緒にねっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:30.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気がつけば 夢中になってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:35.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「そういうコトあるよね」って言ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:41.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キュッと手と手つないだら 伝わる ぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:46.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこにでも行けちゃう気がしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tin-Ton-Tan 踏み出した瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:58.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界がパノラマみたいにひらけたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:03.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile こんな空の広さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:09.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人きりじゃ きっと気づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:14.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 笑顔こだましてる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:22.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸に広がる やさしい うれしい あたらしい予感たち
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:27.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一歩一歩進んで行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:04.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 多麼不可思議 是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:12.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你微笑 心中就像繁星般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's little step! 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:17.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's feel skip! 一起來呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:30.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來 已經沉浸其中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:35.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你對我說 「常有的事情！」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:41.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著緊握的雙手 傳來你的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:46.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿能走到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:52.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叮 咚 鐺 邁出一步的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:58.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界像全景照片一樣展現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:03.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 如此廣闊的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:09.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隻身一人 一定不會發現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:14.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tinkling Smile 笑容在迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:22.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿內心的溫柔和喜悅 還有新的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:27.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步一步往前走吧！
